room_title: Escape room "Houdini's Workshop" by Clue Chase in New York
review: It was awesome! We almost got out! I want to go back and solve some of the other puzzles for sure! So much to solve!

room_title: Escape room "Houdini's Workshop" by Clue Chase in New York
review: So much fun! I had such a humorous and friendly guide, and her timely tips were just right for aiding our puzzles without giving them away!Highly recommend.
